kpi_info.title: TRANSFERRED DATA FOR CS STREAMING IN UL
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU CS streaming data in SRNC in the uplink direction measured during the measurement interval. UPDATED: The counter is updated at 20-second intervals. If the UE is in softer handover, then the counter is updated for only one cell once per each BTS.
